    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/ab39209570cdb180e9e1532c18d11c9a.poster.avif?t=1723116550\" width=672 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/ab39209570cdb180e9e1532c18d11c9a.webm?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/ab39209570cdb180e9e1532c18d11c9a.mp4?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>El Mono is the game that will finally <strong>enable your fantasy of being an uncontrollable animal</strong> let loose into a civilian crowd. Tap into it's simplistic first-person interface and take full control of man-kind's most powerful predecessor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/7d3b647b933af81f4848b23c47bc3721.poster.avif?t=1723116550\" width=672 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/7d3b647b933af81f4848b23c47bc3721.webm?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/7d3b647b933af81f4848b23c47bc3721.mp4?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After years of research and development <strong>the perfect crowd simulation has arrived</strong>. Terrorize over 256 persons with all the blood and knockback that you deserve.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/e9e9215faaa7c740f3b32c9b889ace24.poster.avif?t=1723116550\" width=672 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/e9e9215faaa7c740f3b32c9b889ace24.webm?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060580/extras/e9e9215faaa7c740f3b32c9b889ace24.mp4?t=1723116550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Independently controlled arms? Visible torso? Procedural leg animations? We have it all. <strong>The most immersive monkey game</strong> is here.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extra Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Impress your friends and family with obligatory monkey facts every time you die.<br></li><li> Go against the world on the official El Mono Global Leaderboard.<br></li><li> And what's a monkey game without bananas? It's not, that's what.</li></ul>",
